   <TR ALIGN="CENTER">
      <TD>Taj Mahal</TD>
      <TD>
<font  size = "5" face = "Calibri" color = "#FF7F50">
Since it is one of the wonders of the world, the Taj Mahal is one of the most well known monuments in the world. <br> It is a perfect destination for a romantic holiday, considering its historical background. <br> Built in the Mughal times, this monument was not only considered to be beautiful but also a great architectural acheivement.
<br>For more information <a href="https://whc.unesco.org/en/list/252">click here</a>  
