   <TR ALIGN="CENTER">
      <TD>Lotus Temple</TD>
      <TD>
<font  size = "5" face = "Calibri" color = "#FFFFFF">
The India Gate is a memorial to the soldiers of the British Indian Army who died during the various wars that took place between 1914 and 1921. <br> It is a perfect destination for a historical holiday, considering the importance of the Indian struggle that it represents. <br> Located in the heart of New Delhi, the surroundings of the India Gate are truly breathtaking.
<br>For more information <a href="https://www.india.com/news-travel/5-interesting-facts-about-the-bahai-lotus-temple-in-delhi-that-you-must-know-3232502/">click here</a> 
