      <TD>
<font  size = "5" face = "Calibri" color = "#32CD32">
Around the world the Lotus Temple is known for its unique flower-like shape. <br> It aims to promote the Bahai faith, which beelives in the oneness of People, Religions and Gods. <br> The temple is visited by millions of people evrey year and it is defintely a destination that should be on your list when you visit India.
